title: FDIC, 4th Qtr 2008 Savings banks regulated by OTS, USA, 2009
name: FDIC, 4th Qtr 2008 Savings banks regulated by OTS, USA, 2009
description: The point shapefile shows the geocoded banking data released by FDIC on 25th Feb, 2008. These are the banks who are regulated by OTS (Office of Thrift Supervision), the data shows bank performance for the 4th quarter of 2008. Also included are Foreign banks insured by respective foreign govenments. See elsewhere on GC data on banks regulated by FDIC (Office of Comptroller and Currency), OCC (Office of Comptroller and Currency) and Fed Reserve.
